# Copy to `.env.local` and fill what you need. None are required in MVP.
#
# Anthropic key is stored in expo-secure-store at runtime via the settings
# screen — NOT via env. Setting it here would leak it into the JS bundle.
#
# Reserved for future remote-log sink (Sentry, Axiom, etc.):
# GARDEN_LOG_SINK_URL=
# GARDEN_LOG_SINK_TOKEN=
